"{\"uid\": \"cyclingnews.com-news-how-to-watch-olympics-cycling-keirin-live-streams-at-paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  A guide to watching the chaotic sprint event from August 7-11  When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission.Here's how it works.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 166, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 168, \"to\": 270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are now subscribed  Your newsletter sign-up was successful  One of the curiosities of the track racing programme at theParis Olympic Gamesis the Keirin, where riders are paced behind a motorbike before sprinting for the line.\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 421, \"end\": 427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7595095610426944e-58, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Starting out on August 7 and culminating on August 11, here's how to watch an Olympics 2024 Keirin live stream.\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 594, \"end\": 600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7595095610426944e-58, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Keirin originated in Japan and was first included in the Olympics in 2000 as one of the sprinting events.\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 619, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7595095610426944e-58, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}, {\"begin\": 640, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999997739560313, \"rank\": 1.7724925350428662e-07, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Riders start out following a 'derny' - a motorbike that's powered these days by electricity - which winds them up to speed over the course of three laps, and then leaves them to fight it out among themselves for another three laps.\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dates:August 7-11  Free streams:CBC(Canada),BBC(UK),Channel 9(Australia)  USA:Peacock TV  Canada:CBC,TSN,Sportsnet  UK:BBC,Discovery+  Australia:Channel 9  Watch anywhere:TryNordVPN, 100% risk-free  The Keirin favours the strongest sprinters, and often the best riders in the Individual Sprint will double up.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.111968130950043e-13, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.110767104817177e-14, \"text\": \"TSN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 1074, \"end\": 1076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999825422493, \"rank\": 1.7443845759172576e-08, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9997457468269308, \"rank\": 0.00025429522886985165, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 2.1476627036864666e-12, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7595095610426944e-58, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}, {\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5073004860304886e-20, \"text\": \"Sprint\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the chaotic nature of the Keirin makes it a bit more of a lottery, with the format still a popular gambling attraction in Japan.\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7595095610426944e-58, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}, {\"begin\": 1399, \"end\": 1404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999997739560313, \"rank\": 1.7724925350428662e-07, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Harrie Levreyson had to settle for bronze in Tokyo but the Dutc