h was eventuallywon by Ellesse Andrews(New Zealand).\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1635, \"end\": 1641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7595095610426944e-58, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}, {\"begin\": 1711, \"end\": 1726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellesse_Andrews\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ellesse Andrews\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellesse_Andrews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellesse_Andrews\"}, {\"begin\": 1727, \"end\": 1738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6574037309897949, \"rank\": 0.47113542308626744, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's Keirin got underway on Saturday August 10 with the first round, with all favourites through, and the action comes to a head on August 11.\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1752, \"end\": 1758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7595095610426944e-58, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The quarterfinals are at 11:29, the semifinals at 12:29, and the finals at 13:23 - all local time (CET).\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1989, \"end\": 1992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_European_Time\", \"score\": 0.999997390917308, \"rank\": 2.6090894580040385e-06, \"text\": \"CET\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_European_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_European_Time\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This guide explains how to watch Olympics Cycling Keirin 2024 wherever you are in the world, including details ofhow to use a VPNif you are away from home.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more from the track, find outhow to watch Track Cyclingat the Paris Olympics, and for more from the other disciplines, find outhow to watch cycling at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2326, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC holds the broadcasting rights for the Olympic Games in the USA.\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2328, \"end\": 2331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9855230282391247, \"rank\": 0.014689622988997094, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2391, \"end\": 2394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"score\": 0.9996040674772165, \"rank\": 0.00039608934735226357, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics will be shown across several of the the broadcaster's television channels, and also on the network's streaming service,Peacock.\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2528, \"end\": 2535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999992034744071, \"rank\": 7.965250480028209e-07, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rounds of the men's and women's Keirin will be available on Peacock, which offers a seven-day free trial for those who want to try before they buy.\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2678, \"end\": 2684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7595095610426944e-58, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}, {\"begin\": 2706, \"end\": 2713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999992034744071, \"rank\": 7.965250480028209e-07, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A full subscription to the service via Peacock Premium starts from $7.99 per month.\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2833, \"end\": 2848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peacock_(streaming_service)\", \"score\": 0.9999999936162567, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Peacock Premium\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peacock_(streaming_service)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peacock_(streaming_service)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ad-free Peacock Premium Plus costs $13.99 per month.\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's final will be digital-only on Peacock but the men's final on August 11 is also set to be shown live on television, on NBC 4 New York.\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 3081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3066, \"end\": 3080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC 4 New York\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\"}, {\"begin\": 3066, \"end\": 3069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9855230282391247, \"rank\": 0.014689622988997094, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 3066, \"end\": 3080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC 4 New York\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC 4 New York is available via cable plans, but there is no need to worry if you do not have cable.Slingis a smart TV service that allows people in the US to watch cable channels on their TV, laptop or tablet without actually having to subscribe to an annual cable TV package.\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3083, \"end\": 3086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9855230282391247, \"rank\": 0.014689622988997094, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 3083, \"end\": 3097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC 4 New York\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\"}, {\"begin\": 3083, \"end\": 3097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC 4 New York\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\"}, {\"begin\": 3236, \"end\": 3238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 0.9999984756321078, \"rank\": 1.5243700793281793e-06, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC 4 New York is available to New Yorkers on Sling with the Sling Blue package, which costs $40 per month ($20 for the first month).\", \"from\": 3361, \"to\": 3494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3361, \"end\": 3375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC 4 New York\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WNBC\"}, {\"begin\": 3361, \"end\": 3364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9855230282391247, \"rank\": 0.014689622988997094, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 3422, \"end\": 3427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sling_TV\", \"score\": 0.9999999868655324, \"rank\": 1.3134358373563745e-08, \"text\": \"Sling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sling_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sling_TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Australia, cycling fans can watch the Olympics for free onChannel 9and its9Now streaming service- arguably the most comprehensive free Olympics coverage in the world.\", \"from\": 3496, \"to\": 3665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3499, \"end\": 3508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 2.1476627036864666e-12, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As is the case in other territories, a good chunk of the action is expected to be included in live television broadcast, but for guaranteed coverage of all the Keirin racing, fans can head to 9Now on the smart device of their choosing.\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3827, \"end\": 3833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7595095610426944e-58, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you live in Canada, you can catch the Olympics across several broadcasters, including the free-to-air CBC, and subscription services TSN and Sportsnet.\", \"from\": 3904, \"to\": 4058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3919, \"end\": 3925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.111968130950043e-13, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 4040, \"end\": 4043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.110767104817177e-14, \"text\": \"TSN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not clear whetherCBCwill show the Keirin as part of its daily television output; that may depend on how the Canadian cyclists fare.\", \"from\": 4060, \"to\": 4196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4099, \"end\": 4105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7595095610426944e-58, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}, {\"begin\": 4173, \"end\": 4181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\", \"score\": 0.9998962672703284, \"rank\": 0.00010374347001092558, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The finals are set to be streamed online onCBC Gem.\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Access to the broadcaster's ad-free premium library costs $5.99 per month, though the ad-supported version is free of charge.\", \"from\": 4249, \"to\": 4374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TSN and Sportsnet do not have dedicated streams for each sport, so it's not certain whether the Keirin will make the cut as part of their programming.\", \"from\": 4376, \"to\": 4526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4376, \"end\": 4379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.110767104817177e-14, \"text\": \"TSN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Sports_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 4472, \"end\": 4478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7595095610426944e-58, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheTSNsubscription service will set you back $19.99 per month or $199.90 per year.\", \"from\": 4528, \"to\": 4610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, aSportsnet SN Nowsubscription costs $14.99 per month or $179.99 per year.\", \"from\": 4611, \"to\": 4695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4633, \"end\": 4635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sportsnet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.2570931905099435e-21, \"text\": \"SN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sportsnet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sportsnet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the UK, cycling fans will be able to watch the Olympics on the BBC for free, via BBC One, BBC Two andBBC iPlayer.\", \"from\": 4697, \"to\": 4813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4704, \"end\": 4706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999825422493, \"rank\": 1.7443845759172576e-08, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 4763, \"end\": 4766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9997457468269308, \"rank\": 0.00025429522886985165, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC only has rights to broadcast two streams at any one time, however, so while the track cycling will be heavily favoured by the national broadcaster, it's not guaranteed that every round of the Keirin will be shown.\", \"from\": 4815, \"to\": 5036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4819, \"end\": 4822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9997457468269308, \"rank\": 0.00025429522886985165, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 5015, \"end\": 5021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7595095610426944e-58, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For that, you will have to watch onDiscovery+, home to the most comprehensive coverage in the UK - 3,800 hours of live action across 55 channels.\", \"from\": 5038, \"to\": 5183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5132, \"end\": 5134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999825422493, \"rank\": 1.7443845759172576e-08, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks to aspecial Olympics dealyou can subscribe to the \\\"standard\\\" Discovery+ package for a cut-price \\u00a33.99 per month - sign up before August 11 and you can take advantage of the lower price until the end of the year.\", \"from\": 5185, \"to\": 5403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The package includes year-round cycling streams as well as other live sports, including snooker, tennis, motorsports, and more.\", \"from\": 5404, \"to\": 5531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are traveling abroad and try to access your usual live streaming services to watch the action, you may find your access to be geo-restricted.\", \"from\": 5533, \"to\": 5681, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In this case, a VPN service will come in handy, allowing your computer to pretend it's home and let you log into your streaming accounts to catch all of the racing action.\", \"from\": 5683, \"to\": 5854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our colleagues atTechRadarthoroughly tested several VPNservices and NordVPN won the gold medal:  NordVPN - get the world's favorite VPNWe've put all the major VPNs through their paces and we rate NordVPN as the best for streaming Netflix as our top pick, thanks to its speed, ease of use and strong security features.\", \"from\": 5856, \"to\": 6173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6086, \"end\": 6093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.488888717370993e-33, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's also compatible with just about any streaming device out there, including Amazon Fire TV Stick, Apple TV, Xbox and PlayStation, as well as Android and Apple mobiles.\", \"from\": 6174, \"to\": 6344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6253, \"end\": 6273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Fire_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amazon Fire TV Stick\", \"types\": [\"Q1067263\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Fire_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Fire_TV\"}, {\"begin\": 6275, \"end\": 6283, \"title\": \